    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with medium model influence and high decision consequence. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is supported by the validated model outputs across all 5 COU operating points.",
